##  Translation 

* The tablet is written in Seki (the native language of [Yezuha](/yezuha/)). It can be translated by [Rekke](/rekke/) after he learns [Aedyran](/aedyran/) (this takes 30 days from his rescue):
{{Description|"Prince of the Heavens shall be fed only young grasses grown on the hills of Lipasalis. He shall be curried morning and night with a brush made of the bristles of boars fed on golden root..."

"He shall be given to only the handsomest of mares of the most feisty temperament, for he grows bored unless challenged. And when he is sad, he shall have in his ear whispered only the sweetest praise."}}
